<text>
  <centered> Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</centered>
  <book>Caturārakkhadīpanī</book>
  <subhead>Kāyapaccavekkhaṇā</subhead>
  <paragraph nr="1">. Dussīlakathā,</paragraph>
  <paragraph nr="2">. Sīlānisaṃsakathā,</paragraph>
  <paragraph nr="3">. Anūsāsanakathā,</paragraph>
  <paragraph nr="4">. Āvāsikācārakathā,</paragraph>
  <paragraph nr="5">. Paccayanissaggakathā,</paragraph>
  <paragraph nr="6">. Pātimokkhakathā,</paragraph>
  <paragraph nr="7">. Dāyakovādakathā,</paragraph>
  <subhead>Paṇāmapaṭiñā</subhead>
  <hangnum nr="1"/>
  <gatha type="1"> Cakkavāḷa  nahutā ga, devāli gaṇa cumbito;</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Buddha pādambujo ṭhātu, sīse dayā tigandhajo.</gatha>
  <hangnum nr="2"/>
  <gatha type="1"> Nanta  cakkavāḷa bbhugga, guṇa sanniccitaṃ jinaṃ;</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Vande tappūjitaṃ dhammaṃ, tajjaṃ saṅghañca nimmalaṃ.</gatha>
  <hangnum nr="3"/>
  <gatha type="1"> Vakkhāmi  caturārakkhaṃ, sambuddha vacana nvayaṃ;</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Appamādāvahaṃ etaṃ, sottabbaṃ bhavabhīruhi.</gatha>
  <hangnum nr="4"/>
  <gatha type="1"> Buddhānussati  maraṇā, bhubhā mettāca bhāvanā;</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Appamādāya ārakkhā, catasso mānitā sataṃ.</gatha>
  <paragraph nr="1">. Buddhānūssati bhāvanā,</paragraph>
  <paragraph nr="2">. Maraṇassati bhāvanā,</paragraph>
  <paragraph nr="3">. Asubha bhāvanā,</paragraph>
  <paragraph nr="4">. Mettā bhāvanā,</paragraph>
  <hangnum nr="5"/>
  <gatha type="1"> Buddhovādaṃ  saritvāva, maccubbiggā sukhesino;</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Sītā sītataraṃ yanti, subhamettambusi-ṭṭhitā.</gatha>
  <hangnum nr="6"/>
  <gatha type="1"> Maraṇaggi vāraṇambu, sambuddhavacanaṃ yidaṃ;</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Bahū tadaggi santattā, sītāvāsuṃ tadambunā.</gatha>
  <hangnum nr="7"/>
  <gatha type="1"> Saddhaṃ  buddhena tejetvā, mānaṃ maraṇacintayā;</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Asubhāya hane rāgaṃ, dosaṃ mettāya paññavā.</gatha>
</text>
